Courtenay Taylor https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Courtenay_Taylor 0 Courtenay Kellen Taylor (born July 19, 1969) is an American voice actress, known for her roles as Jack in Mass Effect 2 and 3, Ada Wong in the Resident Evil series, the title character in OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes and the female Sole Survivor in Fallout 4.
